            "question": {
                "text": "Consider three machines M, N and P with IP \naddresses 100.10.5.2, 100.10.5.5, and 100.10.5.6 \nrespectively. \nThe \nsubnet \nmask \nis \nset \nto \n255.255.255.252 for all the three machines. Which \none of the following is true?",
